summary: we getting cheesy about jaspar?? count me tf in!! I found caspar first when he collabed with someone I dont watch anymore, thru...
question: we getting cheesy about jaspar?? count me tf in!! I found caspar first when he collabed with someone I dont watch anymore, thru caspar I found joe. ok I lied imma get cheesy about joe. I went thru a particularly hard time in 2014-15 and I just watched his videos to laugh and take my mind off things. now I kind of associate him with my sad days but I appreciate him and caspar and I love them with my whole ass heart ~end speech~
answer:
Okay so first I don’t know why but the way you wrote all that made me laugh, so thank you for that! 😂

Then, that’s kinda sad Joe reminds you of a sad time, even though I am glad he helped you go through that. And I am extremely happy to hear you talk about it this way because it seems you have gone out of that hard phase, and this is something that really warms my heart.

I’ve seen so many times people saying Youtubers (talking about youtubers in general, not only Jaspar here.) helped them, or still help, go through hard times and knowing that really makes me happy and proud! This is really important to me to see them help others and offer smiles, laughs and support to those who need it.

I love Joe and Caspar so much as well, and I just associate them with a very bright moment of my life, not that the period was the best, just that when I was watching them, I couldn’t feel anything but happy! (Here I am, being super cheesy again.)

Anyway, thank you for your message! If any of you also want to share something like this with me (or anything, of course!), please go ahead! 🌹
